uk.ac.ox.cs.diadem.oxpath.core.domlookup

Interface DOMLookup

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DOMLookupByRobustXPath, DOMLookupByUniqueXPath, DOMLookupDocumentPosition

    public interface DOMLookup
    These interface specifies classes that compensate for an issue (observed in Mozilla), where DOM references perpetuate after new pages are loaded and the old page is revisited by invoking browser.back(). Prepare references with getNodeReferences(nodes). Retrieve new nodes via a call to getRenderedNode(staleNode,newDocument).
    Author:
    AndrewJSel, Giovanni Grasso
